XREF_MATRIX_2:framework/claude/skills/sdd-roadmap/SKILL.md->refs/{design,impl,review,run,revise,crud}.md
XREF_MATRIX_3:framework/claude/skills/sdd-roadmap/refs/run.md->refs/{impl,review}.md;framework/claude/skills/sdd-roadmap/refs/review.md->run.md
